## 🛠️ Getting Started

### 📦 Prerequisites
- Node.js v18 or higher

### 🧪 Installation & Run
```bash
# Clone your GitHub Classroom repo
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/your-repo.git
cd your-repo

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run the dev server
npm run dev
